channel.title: Help! Client cannot be applied!
channel.description:
Heres my error that im getting when i try to put correct godsword animation/gfx into my server,
Client.java:17047: BGSSpecial() in client cannot be applied to (int) BGSSpecial(590); ^
Client.java:17058: SGSSpecial() in client cannot be applied to (int) SGSSpecial(656); ^
Client.java:17069: AZGSSpecial() in client cannot be applied to (int) AGSpecial(651); ^
Client.java:17091: ZGSSpecial() in client cannot be applied to (int) ZGSSpecial(592); ^
Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 4 errors Finished! Press any key to continue...
PLEASE HELP! THANKS!

item.dc:creator: @hidendra Hidendra
item.description:
@hidendra wrote:

The method is ZGSSpecial() not ZGSSpecial(int), so you use ZGSSpecial(); instead of ZGSSpecial(592);
[ same for the others. ]
